<doc id="554198" wikidata="Q7617588" url="?curid=554198" title="Stirling and Falkirk">
<text>Stirling and Falkirk is a lieutenancy area of Scotland. It consists of the local government areas of Stirling and Falkirk,
which cover the same areas as the previous districts from 1975 to 1996.

==References==
* The Lord-Lieutenants (Scotland) Order 1996, Statutory Instrument 1996 No. 731 (S.83).</text><links>
